Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞞著大家能看見妖怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  傘飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啦  就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡啊  哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  大概看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看見我嗎  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,260)\fs80}淺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,500)\fs80}蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(588,510)\fs80}{\c&H0025000}的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,525)\fs80}琴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不想碰人類  迫不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真沒耐性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鈣 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我竟會…明明是人類還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  不管了  這個身體我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  銅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類啊  請原諒他的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全是為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葫蘆裡傳出了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  別說話  會累的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  我聽過這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高貴的妖怪們聚集的幻之裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畿月森林裡有一位美麗的蒼琴師叫「淺蔥」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個淺蔥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但她身體抱恙以至無法繼續彈琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送回了故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是面帶笑容的人  完全沒了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人類的孩子啊  為了淺蔥你暫時將身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽話我就咬掉你的耳朵或鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手  低級的  他是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狸貓咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許笑  地藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易接近妖怪肯定沒好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況還要我借出身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是面帶笑容的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得有點可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是早上才回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你的頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛的顏色好像也變藍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  早啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…早  北本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇…嚇我一跳  一瞬間還以為認錯了人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  這兩人在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的辭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一瞬間把夏目看成女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是我的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說北本  田沼感覺到什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:07:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你睡覺時讓淺蔥進入了你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像同化得很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  暫時請你合作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晨的藍色頭髮和眼睛就是附身現象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我叫他別這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無法阻止  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音…你就是淺蔥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要責備他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她從你身體裡出來的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了強行驅逐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能去實現淺蔥的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望得到滿足就會自然離開你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光說也沒用  趕快實現願望讓我們回去吧  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪來的  叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有講給人類聽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你現在起就叫蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼傘的蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接我們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這狸貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的名字  太好了呢  蛇眼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  怎麼連你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  不是很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才身體被佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你的  彈了琴就會離開我的身體了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要從製作琴開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為是特別的琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種額頭上有白線  跟鯉魚長得一樣  叫拉絲的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要抓魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？少廢話  別擺出副鬱悶的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥和蛇眼是什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  蛇眼是負責撐傘的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐傘？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畿月森林聚集了主人壬生大人看上的有才之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡為壬生大人和大家撐傘  並保護他們是蛇眼的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼很能幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畿月像夢境一般美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永遠留在那裡  一直待在壬生大人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠  永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能彈琴了就趕出來  真是心胸狹窄的神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是壬生大人收留了無處可去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了自己沒用  我離開了那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  這就是拉絲  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這就是要用來做琴弦的線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那材料收集就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  接下來是琴身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找樹墩  而且上面要長著剛發芽的竹筍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下  再等一下就能讓你彈琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼真的對淺蔥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了  全身濕成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  貴志會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  好好擦乾  真的都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永遠留在那裡  永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好剛空出來  快去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在這裡待到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是…夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是淺蔥的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了嗎  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  淺蔥她睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想跟她說話的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥的手指已經不能彈琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體像乾枯的泥土一樣剝落的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但進入別的容器時惡化會變慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一次看到她笑是在壬生大人面前彈琴  一臉幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在演奏中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚突然開始剝落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白修長的手指和發光的臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在憧憬不已的壬生大人面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是滿月  通往畿月的路會打開一會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想最後讓她在壬生大人面前彈一次琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前請讓她借用你的力量  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼為什麼…為什麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  銅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個撐傘的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真的有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長竹子的樹墩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在催情草的草叢中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我跟什麼說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你了哦  作為交換我要拿走你的腸子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  跟奇怪的妖怪說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  你在好好地找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起  夏目  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  趕快動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體開始不舒服了  這種無力有點發熱的感覺是淺蔥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼弱的身體還去演奏  淺蔥的生命會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  真對不起  都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我都沒確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥你想彈琴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還有一次機會  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不靈巧  手指僵硬可能彈不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅他一直  一直對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅  怎麼了  到底要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  現在通往畿月的路還開放著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  然後為壬生大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好的  我來取你的腸子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴  淺蔥和蛇眼重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那傢伙趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  多虧你的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎  現在還能趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的話我來抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是蛇眼  受了這樣的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能彈我想再彈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只為那位大人彈著琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果能再彈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為了溫柔的  我重要的朋友你彈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅  你能聽我彈琴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠處聽到了音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未聽見過的美麗音符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:20:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音符從我的指尖流出  劃開空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像降落到空中一般  淺蔥離開了我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶淺蔥回故鄉去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是睡得很深很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見了  淺蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡了啊  老師  在人家辛苦的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服了嗎  你這個爛好人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了  去給我買包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七辻屋還沒開門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師有過想永遠待下去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方我一輩子都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來一直這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  別抱我  放開  還不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著彈了留下的琴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那美麗的音符不再出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那音符不是出自我的手指  是出自她的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:50.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}貓咪徒然帳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師  你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我出去  夏目這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我掉進了洞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天上掉下隻白色小豬


